xt": "is a dial. var. thereof; (Yaakoob, S;) the former being of the dial. of Kureysh, (Yaakoob, accord. to the TA,) or of Keys, (M in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "q$T", "text_ar": "قشط"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",) and the latter of the dial. of Temeem and Asad; the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "k", "text_ar": "ك"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "not being a substitute for the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "q", "text_ar": "ق"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Yaakoob, TA:) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Astk$T", "text_ar": "استكشط", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies the same. (Ham., p. 693.) It is said in the Kur, [lxxxi. 11,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waA_i*aA Als~amaA='u ku$iTato", "text_ar": "وَاـِذَا السَّمَا=ءُ كُشِطَتْ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And when the heaven shall be removed from its place, like as a roof is removed from its place;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Zj, K;) and in like manner"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qu$iTatN", "text_ar": "قُشِطَتٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Zj, S, *) accord. to the reading of 'Abd-Allah [Ibn-Mes'ood]: (S:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "shall be pulled off and folded together."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Fr.) And you say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ka$aTa AlHarofa", "text_ar": "كَشَطَ الحَرْفَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He removed the letter from its place."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ku$iTa rawoEuhu", "text_ar": "كُشِطَ رَوْعُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ki$aATN", "text_ar": "كِشَاطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K, * TA,) (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "His fright,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fear, became removed;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, * TA;) and so ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ank$T", "text_ar": "انكشط", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rwEh", "text_ar": "روعه"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA:) or the latter signifies (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "his fright,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fear, went away."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ka$aTa", "text_ar": "كَشَطَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ald~aAb~aha", "text_ar": "الدَّابَّهَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qa$aTahaA", "text_ar": "قَشَطَهَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He removed the housing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "covering, from the beast of carriage"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "q$T", "text_ar": "قشط"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ka$aTotu AlbaEiyra", "text_ar": "كَشَطْتُ البَعِيرَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, Msb,) aor. as above, (Msb,) and so the inf. n., (S, Msb,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I skinned the camel:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb:) you should not say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "salaxotu", "text_ar": "سَلَخْتُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; for the Arabs, in speaking of a camel, say only"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ka$aTotuhu", "text_ar": "كَشَطْتُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jal~adotuhu", "text_ar": "جَلَّدْتُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "Msb", "K", "MS", "TA"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}